9:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"80 90年代嘅私樓通常都有勁深嘅窗台俗稱發水樓 實際真係用到嘅面積唔多 而且有機會五門歸心 傢俬擺位難過居屋 而依家新落成嘅私樓通常發水喺露台同埋工作平台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7252201a1b6dfcb38c1e5e6d9a0c72d6b2171f","tid":1909334,"uid":261566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f208a06f39cefb368b0172908e48042d23770b13","tid":1909334,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3b454501c0e0155737283c1a033aa0d307c5acc","tid":1909334,"uid":261566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7e37ebafeaec7cdf691ba3b732aa69c3188dbdac","tid":1909334,"uid":112845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:24:38.000Z","msg":"80 90年代嘅私樓通常都有勁深嘅窗台俗稱發水樓 實際真係用到嘅面積唔多 而且有機會五門歸心 傢俬擺位難過居屋 而依家新落成嘅私樓通常發水喺露台同埋工作平台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"新例後實用面積定義唔同咗 唔包括咗好多嘢例如窗台等等 依家一手二手都係賣實用面積 好少再講建築面積 所以依家實用率嘅參考價值唔高 反而個則影響左個實用感 但係新樓實用面積包埋露台工作平台各種發水位 最好睇清楚呢啲位"},{"pid":"673c3e118c2649c07e1dbe98a9215f894ca86906","tid":1909334,"uid":289946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"大西北日日來回三個鐘，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69f20b2b18eebd83275717ed13c011de3b737db","tid":1909334,"uid":130209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T12:03:48.000Z","msg":"真係要睇係咩屋苑<br />\n講環境居屋未必一定差私樓未必一定好<br />\n自己住緊大型居屋， 樓下綠化做得好好<br />\n冇會所冇得bbq但有4，5個游樂場<br />\n冇健身室冇壁球場但有3個羽毛球場， 4張兵兵波檯<br />\n管理費都係個一個二銀錢到到但保養做得好好屋苑好多錢剩<br />\n隔離鄰舍都唔係咩高質&quot;有錢人&quot;但個個都好nice冇痴線佬<br />\n私樓都住過，係有2個比較明顯既優點<br />\n第一係保安， 宜家好多私樓都有雙層保安<br />\n即係入屋苑一個樓下一個， 冇爭人錢怕比收數佬搞既我覺得唔係太重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二係泳池， 公共泳池通常會起係山卡啦地方， 要游水始終冇就咁落樓下游咁方便"},{"pid":"8d5f813500998caa40f034fadb7a9223d9aafe8b","tid":1909334,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"荃西私樓定市區居屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e9e101ce10fa6cc0bc9670d03035e3baa99b9a","tid":1909334,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44bb9fb7ec6b6eb5fdf578ff328cca30bb1cff1","tid":1909334,"uid":45914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:09.000Z","msg":"九龍"},{"pid":"c61bac6f429f2e8e49ca2f245589f8b2ba35a2f6","tid":1909334,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5226b2bd223e8a146b3c3609815c2522c5cace7f","tid":1909334,"uid":241101,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1b4e7ece26fb79b699f2522fddcf02e4d6eac865","tid":1909334,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:26:32.000Z","msg":"市區康山花園<br />\n大西北嘉湖山莊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"冇得比喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差幾級<br />\n起碼都要攞溱柏、采葉庭、PY呢啲半新近郊先有得比"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"差好遠喎 一定係康山⋯⋯"},{"pid":"3068d3318bbce17c1b072a2e4cdee18b8ef205fe","tid":1909334,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d5f813500998caa40f034fadb7a9223d9aafe8b","tid":1909334,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"荃西私樓定市區居屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=